original: Danielsson, Karl Olof, apotekare, Söderköping, f. 30/3/01 i Byarum, Jönköp. 1. G. 36 m. Gun Josefsson. Barn: Eva f. 37, Inga 39. — Farm. kand. 23, apot:ex. 27. Anst. å apot. i Uddevalla 19-25 o. 27-31, å apot. Kronan i Borås 31-38, priv. å apot. på Tjörn 38-46, å apot. Kronan i Söderköping ised. 46.
translated: Danielsson, Karl Olof, pharmacist, Söderköping, b. March 30, 1901 in Byarum, Jönköping. 1st marriage in 1936 with Gun Josefsson. Children: Eva b. 1937, Inga b. 1939. - Bachelor of Pharmacy (Pharm. kand.) in 1923, pharmacist exam in 1927. Employed at a pharmacy in Uddevalla from 1919-1925 and in 1927-1931, at Kronan pharmacy in Borås 1931-1938, privately at a pharmacy on Tjörn 1938-1946, and at Kronan pharmacy in Söderköping since 1946.
